ldapLogin()

Description
    bool ldapLogin(string $username, string $password, object $engine)
    Connects to the LDAP server and performs a check on the user's name, group and OU.  Sets $_SESSION variables based on the results of these checks.

Parameters
    username
	A string containing a username.
    password
	A string containing a password.
    engine
	The engine object.

Return Values
    Returns TRUE on completion.

See Also
    ldapConnect()
